articles.title: ‘Baby Reindeer’s’ Alleged Real Martha Denies Stalking Claims on ‘Piers Morgan’: ‘I Didn’t Write Him the Emails…I Think He Probably Made Them Up Himself’ - Variety
articles.description: The real Martha from 'Baby Reindeer' has been revealed.
articles.content:
